  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluate radiation exposure and procedure times for continuous fluoroscopic monitoring during
      lumbar ESI
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this prospective study was to evaluate radiation exposure and procedure times
      for fluoroscopic monitoring during lumbar ESI with analyzing the differences among operators
      (experienced staff and trainee) and among different method for ESI.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
